{"tid":1115551,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"「改歌」許志安 - 壞左既人","createTime":"2019-04-19T09:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T11:09:37.000Z","uid":28054,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7d49893b1ea56c0b998697c81bca7feca68342","tid":1115551,"uid":28054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"妳　最賤格的妓女<br />\n淫婦發誓　安心讓我撫摸<br />\n看著妳淫水　早濕到凳底<br />\n願每天抽插享受這身體<br />\n<br />\n我　已是最丟～臉<br />\n全身軟弱　色心卻扯得起<br />\n證據會留低　也在所不計<br />\n甚至call車去鯉魚門射到死<br />\n<br />\n願可為妳　放下我的靈魂<br />\n來親近妳　我未理身後那家妻<br />\n無左自我　我係壞左既人<br />\n別阻住我　背住妳偷食最重要一切"},{"pid":"45781e3595ae2309e2aaf00fad3ad77ed47224d2","tid":1115551,"uid":28054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6db5bbf2b8c4a4ba63ae0701d88e22b62c28df","tid":1115551,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"淫夫發誓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8eabb916b2df5b5a88a37c110f1fa3ab1437f1","tid":1115551,"uid":74980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"盡咗力就得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd59a2ab80c0e3bc1483681bd20a5caa95764d9","tid":1115551,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b8eabb916b2df5b5a88a37c110f1fa3ab1437f1","tid":1115551,"uid":74980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"盡咗力就得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"但係<br />\n有時有d嘢真係冇得勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad4bf54c5c43366866e2cf85733888ce82fd960","tid":1115551,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:09:37.000Z","msg":"唔係丫 幾好笑啊<img src=\"